    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="907860799">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-907860799" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-907860799" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="907860799">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3895215/">铁十字的荣耀</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-03-30</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">天平天国果然是历史的诅咒死后复生；作者多次为宋教仁扼腕，错过了政治现代化、法制现代化的路口，所造成的损失至今无法弥补；</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
